                                    class="text-brand-400 hover:text-brand-300"><code>MpLocalDate</code></a></td>
                <td class="py-2">A calendar date (no time, no timezone)</td>
                <td class="py-2">Birthdays, holidays, billing periods, date pickers</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-white/5">
