                                    class="text-brand-400 hover:text-brand-300"><code>MpLocalDateTime</code></a></td>
                <td class="py-2">A date and time (no timezone)</td>
                <td class="py-2">Calendar events, user-facing display, data entry before timezone is known</td>
            </tr>
